     <h3>Nominations for the Office of Trustee for Ward 2</h3>
      <p>March 18, 21, 22, 23, and 24, 2016 between the hours of 8:30 am - 4:00 pm.</p>
      <a href="#dialog3" name="modal" id="modal">Click here for more information.</a></p>
   	  <div id="dialog3" class="window">
        <h3>
        <center>
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN THAT ON THE FOLLOWING DAYS:</center>
        </h3>
        <p>March 18, 21, 22, 23, and 24th, 2016 between the hours of 8:30 am - 4:00 pm at the following location 1161 St. Claire St., Birtle, MB. I will receive nominations for the office of Trustee for Ward 2 for the Park West School Division. <br />
<br />
Further details may be accessed by contacting SEO Jean Nash, 204-859-2867, or email nash_jean@hotmail.com.<br />
<br />
All nominations shall be made in writing and shall be signed by at least twenty-five voters, or NOT less than 1% of the voters (whichever is the lesser) of the authority or ward (as the case may be), but in all cases by the least two voters. Each nomination shall also be accompanied by the candidate's declaration of qualification. <br />
<br />
Nominations may be filed in person at the above location, on the date and hours specified, by an agent, or by fax. To obtain a nomination paper, and / or candidate's declarationof qualification, contact the SEO. <br />
<br />
<strong>Nomination papers not accompanied by the required documents and not properly filed shall be rejected. </strong>
